        "text": "TO : Director, FBI DATE: July 17, 1947\nFROM : SAC, Los Angeles\nSUBJECT: RECOVERY OF \"FLYING DISC\",\nNORTH HOLLYWOOD, CALIFORNIA,\nJULY 9, 1947"
